      "beast_baseline": "wait i think u got it backwards or something. if i'm starting in eb major, i want to know what major key is related to it. u mentioned c minor, but isn't the relative major of c minor eb major? i'm confused. can u just show me the pattern of how the keys move around the circle? like what's the actual sequence?",
      "beast_suffix": "",
